  "section": "1.3: Unlocking bird runs",
  "stepText": "Teleport to Lumbridge, complete the three RFD quests started earlier. Buy steel gloves. Pick up a second knife for later. Make all your Golovanova fruit tops into botanical pies (cook them right away), prepare five more pie shells. Start The Lost Tribe by speaking to Sigmunt. Start The Ides of Milk, speaking with people along the way for The Lost Tribe and buying 10 bronze axes from Bob along the way. Continue and complete The Ides of Milk, putting the lamp on prayer. Continue The Lost Tribe up to the step where you need to visit Reldo. Cut and burn some oak logs for the diary. Finish Lost City (can convert all but one branch now), bring items to go down the Lumbridge swamp caves.\n",
